│ + genres mod added
│ + moods mod added
│ ∗ CLUI library finalized
│ ∗ On installation, the user gets added to the musicdb group
│ ∗ On installation, the data directories group rights get set to writable
│
┝━ MINOR CHANGES
└───────────────────────────────────────╌╌

